title: Ep 21: Halloween Power Hour ft. Jake
description:
Today's Proceedings:  A very special episode!  Today we catch up with friend of the pod Jake and discuss spooky stories while getting drunk during this Halloween Power Hour.  Come for the frights and stay for the rights!  The right to great quality work on your home projects  from JJ&L Carpentry LLC based out of Mendota, Illinois.
